title: 46 migrants found dead in abandoned trailer in San Antonio
content:
1. 46 migrants found dead in abandoned trailer in San Antonio  KSTP
  2. 50 migrants believed dead after they were found in a semitruck in San Antonio, official says, with others hospitalized  CNN
  3. Texas Gov. Abbott lashes out after 46 migrants found dead in tractor-trailer: 'These deaths are on Biden'  Fox News
  4. At least 62 bodies found inside 18-wheeler  KEYE TV CBS Austin
  5. 46 migrants have been found dead inside a semi-truck in San Antonio and 16 have been hospitalized, authorities say  CNN
